mography, xenobiology, engineering and more. You can choose whether to try and impress or annoy the teachers, and your performance will impact her grades at the end of the term. Just remember to keep watch for those dark forces which might seek to do her harm.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Continue to relive the days of good old fashioned point-and-click adventure games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> About five hours of gameplay for the average player. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Mouse, keyboard and controller support.</p></li></ul>","developers":["Pilgrim Adventures"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/694370/header.jpg?t=1736520575","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256692255,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256692255/movie480.mp4?t=1600078878","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256692255/movie_max.mp4?t=1600078878"},"name":"Preview Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256692255/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1600078878","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256692255/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1600078878","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256692255/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1600078878"}}],"name":"Space Pilgrim Academy: Year 1","package_groups":[{"description":"","display_type":0,"is_recurring_subscription":"false","name":"default","save_text":"","selection_text":"Select a purchase option","subs":[{"can_get_free_license":"0","is_free_license":false,"option_description":"","option_text":"Space Pilgrim Academy - <span class=\"discount_original_price\">$1.99</span> $0.55","packageid":199247,"percent_savings":0,"percent_savings_text":"-72% ","price_in_cents_with_discount":55}],"title":"Buy Space Pilgrim Academy: Year